OL,4,Cover death of 'amazing friend' Liam
OL,5,CPayne
OL,7,FNiall Horan has paid an emotional
OL,8,Ftribute to former One Direction
OL,9,Fbandmate Liam Payne, saying he is
OL,10,F"absolutely devastated" at the loss of
OL,11,Fhis "amazing friend".
OL,13,FPayne, 31, died after falling from a
OL,14,Fhotel balcony in Buenos Aires, where
OL,15,Fhe had been to see Horan's show
OL,16,Fearlier in the month.
