OL,7,FIn a post on Instagram on Friday,
OL,8,FHoran said he will "cherish every
OL,9,Fmoment" they had together, and the
OL,10,Fnews of his passing "doesn't feel
OL,11,Freal".
OL,13,FHe wrote on Instagram: "I'm absolutely
OL,14,Fdevastated about the passing of my
OL,15,Famazing friend, Liam. It just doesn't
OL,16,Ffeel real.
