OL,3,CNiall Horan 'absolutely devastated'
OL,4,Cover death of 'amazing friend' Liam
OL,5,CPayne
OL,7,F"Liam had an energy for life and a
OL,8,Fpassion for work that was infectious.
OL,9,FHe was the brightest in every room and
OL,10,Falways made everyone feel happy and
OL,11,Fsecure.
OL,13,F"All the laughs we had over the years,
OL,14,Fsometimes about the simplest of
OL,15,Fthings, keep coming to mind through
OL,16,Fthe sadness. We got to live out our
OL,17,Fwildest dreams together and I will
OL,18,Fcherish every moment we had forever.
OL,19,FThe bond and friendship we had doesn't
OL,20,Fhappen often in a lifetime.
