OL,5,CPayne
OL,7,F"I feel so fortunate that I got to see
OL,8,Fhim recently. I sadly didn't know that
OL,9,Fafter saying goodbye and hugging him
OL,10,Fthat evening, I would be saying
OL,11,Fgoodbye forever. It's heartbreaking.
OL,13,F"My love and condolences go out to
OL,14,FGeoff, Karen, Ruth, Nicola and of
OL,15,Fcourse his son Bear. Thank you for
OL,16,Feverything, Payno. Love you brother."
