OL,7,FPayne went to the concert with his
OL,8,Fgirlfriend, Kate Cassidy, and posted a
OL,9,Flong thread of videos to his Snapchat
OL,10,Fstories documenting the night,
OL,11,Fincluding one of the couple dancing.
OL,13,FThe band posted a joint statement
OL,14,Fafter Liam Payne's death, saying they
OL,15,Fare "completely devastated" by the
OL,16,Floss of their "brother". It was the
OL,17,Ffirst post on the band's Instagram
OL,18,Faccount in four years.
