OL,5,CPayne
OL,7,FIn a separate statement, Louis
OL,8,FTomlinson, 32, wrote that Payne was
OL,9,F"the most vital part of One Direction"
OL,10,Fand added that he would be telling his
OL,11,Fyoung son Bear "stories of how amazing
OL,12,Fhis dad was".
OL,14,FElsewhere, Zayn Malik said he never
OL,15,Fgot to thank him for supporting him
OL,16,Fthrough "some of the most difficult
OL,17,Ftimes", and that he respected Payne,
OL,18,Fdespite "butting heads" a few times.
