OL,13,FFormer The X Factor judge Sharon
OL,14,FOsbourne has taken shot at the music
OL,15,Findustry for failing Payne, saying "we
OL,16,Fall let you down".
OL,18,FIn a post on Instagram, she wrote:
OL,19,F"Liam, my heart aches. We all let you
OL,20,Fdown".
